The paper deals with natural language understanding and reasoning, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the limitations of current AI systems in physical domains, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The benchmark dataset introduced in the paper requires machine learning techniques for classification and prediction, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The dataset also involves visual perception and understanding, which suggests a connection to computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the potential for future research in robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO).
